# dok-namer categories — Swiss German example.
# Copy this file to categories.yaml and customise it, or point to it with --config.
# If categories.yaml is absent, built-in English defaults are used automatically.
#
# Format: each entry needs a 'key' (= subfolder name under done/)
# and 'keywords' (matched case-insensitively against the final suggested filename).
# The last entry is the catch-all fallback for unmatched files.
